   <p>about it. Thus desiring the Lorde to encrease dayly in you the giftes of his heauenly grace, of worshippe also and health (both of body and minde) that you may still perseuer and goe on forwardes in such onely things as are accepta<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ble to hys holy will: whyche, that you may in deede so doe, I humbly beseeche hym to gyue vnto you abundaunt<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>lye of his holy Spirite. <hi>AMEN.</hi>
   </p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Your Seruaunt. R. HOPER.</signed>
   </closer>
